        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Absolutely. Kit offers free migrations on paid plans. Their team moves your subscribers, automations, forms, and sequences from platforms like Mailchimp, ActiveCampaign, or Beehiiv. Most migrations complete within a few business days, and you don't lose any subscriber data in the process.",
